arStrings.szText: “I found your notice. What work do you have?”
We’ve got a shipment leaving for Skovos in a fortnight. I deal in Khazra glands, but some of my stock spoiled. Now I’m short. Have to get more or I’ll be belly up in the bay. Musk market is ruthless.
Shahos sounds akin to a used car salesmen. A bit shady, but he is being truthful and isn't misleading players.
Luckily for me, some Khazra just wandered from the south and now I have you. Just cut the glands out and I’ll do the rest.
